### ==========================================
### VARIABEL GLOBAL
### (Bisa kamu ganti ID-nya sesuai kebutuhan)
### ==========================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/surat-panggilan

@idSiswaJenifer = 6110dc1d-09d8-4975-b3a6-63fc866897a3
@idSuratTest = fae64e69-06ac-4a40-aab7-6ce29cc23ffe

@idWaka = 8a07c551-c976-44bb-98e4-d17337a3634e
@idGuruBk = e07a985d-583a-44bc-a771-80059a18b5af
@idWalikelas = 16f8168f-77c3-43e4-b522-5e12a17ba6c0


### ==========================================
### 1. KELOMPOK MASTER DATA
### ==========================================

### Ambil Data Siswa (Untuk Dropdown Form)
GET {{baseUrl}}/master/siswa
Accept: application/json

###

### Ambil Data Guru (Untuk Dropdown Penandatangan)
GET {{baseUrl}}/master/guru
Accept: application/json


### ==========================================
### 2. KELOMPOK TRANSAKSI (CRUD SURAT)
### ==========================================

### Buat Surat Panggilan Baru (POST)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_siswa": "{{idSiswaJenifer}}",
  "no_surat": "421.5/002/SMKN3/2026",
  "permasalahan": "Sering bolos pada jam pelajaran produktif dan tidur di kelas.",
  "tanggal_panggilan": "2026-04-10",
  "waktu_panggilan": "09.00 WIB - Selesai",
  "tempat": "Ruang BK SMK Negeri 3 Balige",
  "id_penandatangan": [
    "{{idWaka}}",
    "{{idGuruBk}}",
    "{{idWalikelas}}"
  ]
}

###

### Ambil Riwayat Semua Surat (GET ALL)
GET {{baseUrl}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Hapus Surat (DELETE)
### Ganti variabel idSuratTest dengan ID surat yang mau dihapus
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{idSuratTest}}
Accept: application/json


### ==========================================
### 3. KELOMPOK AKSI / INTEGRASI
### ==========================================

### Generate Link WhatsApp Ortu (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{idSuratTest}}/whatsapp
Accept: application/json

###

### Download PDF Surat (GET)
### ⚠️ CATATAN PENTING:
### Jika kamu klik "Send Request" untuk PDF di VS Code, hasilnya akan berupa teks biner (simbol berantakan)
### karena VS Code tidak bisa merender PDF langsung di tab response.
### Untuk melihat PDF-nya, selalu gunakan BROWSER (Chrome/Edge/Firefox).
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{idSuratTest}}/pdf